                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Hart</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Bogotá</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1902-02-01">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 1, 1902</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Hart acknowledges the receipt of the Department’s telegram of January 22,
                    and requests instructions as to amount of indemnity to be demanded of the
                    Colombian Government.* * *)</p>
            </div>
